reviews.review_msg: Not very subjective on course content, has own ideals on what Aboriginal History is and should be. Mood swings are harsh and she projects her moods at students too frequently.
Not a very nice prof :(  the tests were super hard

I Never got a gradeed test or assignment back. I tried to contact her three times to get a break down of my grades and she never responded. Easiest class I had and the lowest grade I've gotten in university. Students answered my questions in class for her. Biased. Worst prof ever. ps. First Nations history is great(just not prof)
